Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:16.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太过于坐立不安 你总是这么毛毛躁躁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:21.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要装做没有看见 我比任何人都更加爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:24.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你 喜欢你 喜欢你… 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:26.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你 喜欢你 喜欢你… 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:29.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你 喜欢你 喜欢你… 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:32.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你 喜欢你 喜欢你… 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:43.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪的星星让夜色更深沉 梦到的全都是你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:48.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使爱我 你也装得没有似的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:53.33,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你又在迷恋谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:01:04.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 男人们啊 心中总是牵挂着无数的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.45,0:01:14.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 到处都充满了玫瑰色 我心里实在好烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太过于坐立不安 你总是这么毛毛躁躁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:25.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要装做没有看见 我比任何人都更喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.45,0:01:28.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢你哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:36.65,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 夏天的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这里乍看之下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是一个平静的海边村落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少在这位少女开口之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有别人感觉真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想打西瓜耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打西瓜 这个主意蛮不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 “打西瓜”是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐 这是地球人的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话 就让我为你说明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须把眼睛遮住 准备一根木棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过阴险的人就可以金属棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩游戏的人先把眼睛遮住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再把沙滩上的西瓜打烂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在这里没有西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就用诸星当的头代替一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面 面堂 开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 面堂 快把我拉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 把我拉出来 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 这种触感就没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致上就是这种游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有了 有了 就去那里买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 对不起 有没有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:45.13,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盲肠肿胀到了正常的七点五倍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:47.30,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为盲肠肥大症而入院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.61,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伯 给我西瓜 挑一个水分充足的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:52.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 西瓜？你们想把西瓜怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要打西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:03:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打西瓜？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打完了之后要干什么 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西瓜神还没有惩罚你们之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快滚出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不想卖 为什么要摆在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正今天就是不能卖 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 为什么不卖给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是跟他杀价呢 诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…还没杀价就被赶出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因不明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能这样就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是遇到阻挠我的兴致就越高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？西瓜神的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:04:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此叫我们来这里供奉西瓜神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 到底是什么方法的惩罚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会闹出人命还是会毁灭村落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有人清楚所以就更可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正村人害怕受到惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百年来村落的供奉不曾间断
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 曾经发生了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个很爱吃西瓜的青年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是十年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在西瓜供奉日偷吃了西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时幸好发现得早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全村盛大举行供奉才免于惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那名青年腹痛不已 昏迷了十天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹痛不已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过才吃了十个这么大的西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十个？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以面不改色的吃下二十个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以吃十八个左右
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:07:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧 我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这个村落的人是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 怎么了 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大一颗看起来真是不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大一颗味道一定不怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是 色泽也不太漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来就没什么水准
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 达令 为什么把它打扮成这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是它长得太难看 所以放在外头晒太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:07:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答得真妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晒太阳 晒太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么恶心的西瓜还是不要理他 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这里也没意思 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 神体小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 村民们 神体被偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它自己莫名其妙穷追不舍的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青年团出动 女人和小孩快回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护神体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小偷碎尸万断 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 不好了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长 神体被偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长 神体是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被西瓜神所附身的 村子里最大的西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是出了任何差错 村落就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:11:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要去买西瓜又被西瓜追回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一群没有常识的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了 太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:12:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神体裂开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村民们…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村 村长 太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 有一股非常强大的灵气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜大人 请您原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱除恶灵 清除怨灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱除恶灵 清除怨灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱除恶灵 清除…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:12:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大胆 竟然敢把我打破
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村民们觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是村民的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是那些外地小鬼的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真 太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不惩罚所有的村民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愤怒就无法平息了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从你开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你手下留情 西瓜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了 看招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是惩罚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 很可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回敬你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是颗大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敬的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太低级了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到不如生病算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日的落日非常寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夕阳的光芒中的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些脚印正诉说着夏日的黄昏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人凝视着夏日的黄昏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日的歌曲搔弄着耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只要安静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只要闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想用头发感受夏日的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了 夏日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑？我正在感伤之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星也会感伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当讲说种话大家不笑才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过作得到是有板有眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样莫名其妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的一天也快要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最后的夏日里头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望能留下难忘的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天快要结束了 真是罗曼蒂克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 我真的非常的感伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如刚才的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的夏日真是令人难忘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是小忍那独特的体型
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有樱花老师那出色的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“独特的体型”是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要被你想到 就会全身起鸡皮疙瘩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 但是这个夏天什么也没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 现在开始还不会太迟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当真是狗嘴吐不出象牙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是妖怪的周波数
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多待一会好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么突然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什么急事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是想上厕…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是上厕所！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好安静啊 拂面的海风真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来这个夏天真是荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一夜真想静静的感伤一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一首好歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 气氛真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想跟面堂单独的聊一聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望今夜能跟拉姆相依偎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种气氛和旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望能跟小忍在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种喂喂的合音配得真是好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是这种合音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就这样喂喂的结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这么喂喂的离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都要回去了吧 留下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧 都要回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天真会作弄人 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天你这混蛋家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘游艇已经被我包下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？我是感伤的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 太像了 你们是兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…只是眼睛和嘴形太相似了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样 难道我跟妖怪是亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失言了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是妖怪该轮到Cherry出场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:18:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位妖怪有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想跟大家一起感伤一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 大家就好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么看 它都不像是块感伤的料子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在短暂的火花中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了夏日经历的点点滴滴 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女的悲伤 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也跟我一样拥有一颗易碎而天真无邪的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就要结束了 我青春的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是岂有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是珍惜过去的夏日时光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而好好的感伤一番的时刻才对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花老师有点醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上那个人渣也睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天最后的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成熟的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻飘飘的秀发 水汪汪的眼睛 柔嫩的嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂终太郎 现在再不开口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一辈子都会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花老师 我可以坐下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个东西躺在这里 希望你不要踏到他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星 PASS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是流星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脖子不会痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜…喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢吃酸的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 你有喜欢的男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日的恋情是多么残酷而无常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这么悲惨而痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年夏天将会来临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这道单恋的伤痕在夏天来临时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会无情的折磨被抛弃的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个夏天的单恋 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太悲哀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确太悲哀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将结束的夏夜很适合感伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了 看到了
